			Profile
			
			
Dr.XingChenisanassociateprofessoratDepartmentofBiomedicalEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity.HeobtainedhisPh.D.inBiomedicalEngineering&nbsp;in2008.Hehadapost-doctoralexperienceatDepartmentofEpidemiology,DivisionofCancerPrevention,UniversityofTexasM.D.AndersonCancerCenterfromNov.2008toNov.2011.Dr.ChenhasbeenawardedgrantsfromNationalNaturalScienceFoundationofChina,DoctoralFundofMinistryofEducationofChina,andZhejiangKeyScienceandTechnologyInnovationTeam.Hepublishednearly20peerreviewedjournalarticles.Hehasalsoapplied10patentsand6ofthemhavebeenissued.Heisaregularreviewerofmanyjournals,suchasCancerResearch,Cancer,LungCancer,PLoSOne,andInternationalJournalofCancer.

