			Researchwork
			
			Myresearchinterestsincludecancerepidemiologyandprevention,advancedtechnologiesofdetectionofbiomarkers,andtheirapplicationsinclinicalpractice,especiallyintheareaofanearlydetectionoflungcancer.Apartofmyresearchistocollaboratewithhospitalstocarryoutbothprospectiveandcase-controlstudiesoftenonalarge-scale.Wecurrentlyhaveconductedaresearchonlungcancerscreeningcombiningbreathdetectionwithcomputedtomographydetection.Anotherpartofmyresearchfocusontherealizationandoptimizationofdetectiontechnologiesintodesignedmedicalinstrumentsordevices.Wehavecollaboratedwithclinicianstotargetthedevelopingrequirementsandconductedclinicaltrialstoverifytheutilityofthedevices.
			
				
